21 (II) HAS AT LEAST 40 YEARS OF EXPERIENCE AS A CERTIFIED
22 PUBLIC ACCOUNTANT; AND
23 (5) ATTESTS THAT:
24 (I) THE INDIVIDUAL IS RETIRED AND IS NO LONGER ACTIVELY
25 PRACTICING PUBLIC ACCOUNTANCY IN THE STATE; AND
